v.v: Yahweh, you have become the King!
You started to rule as king a very long time ago;
Yahweh, when you created the world, you separated the water from the chaotic mass and formed oceans,
but you are greater than the roar of those oceans,

v: The majesty and the power that you have are like robes that a king wears.
You put the world firmly in place, and it will never be moved out of its place.
and the waves of the waters of those oceans still roar,
more powerful than the ocean waves!
You are Yahweh, the one who is greater than any other god!
and your temple has always been holy.
